North Korea is firmly opposed to unilateral disarmament without trust.
North Korea's foreign minister told the UN on Saturday that the sanctions were exacerbating the country's mistrust of the US, which in such circumstances would absolutely refuse to unilaterally give up its nuclear weapons.
